================================================================================
Static landing-page assets (under site/)
================================================================================

The GitHub Pages landing site at `site/` bundles a few third-party
assets:

- **Star Nest fragment shader** — `site/src/components/StarNest.astro`
  embeds the GLSL "Star Nest" 3D-kaliset shader by Pablo Roman
  Andrioli. Original at https://www.shadertoy.com/view/XlfGRj,
  released under the MIT License.

- **Flying Toasters animation recipe** — `site/src/components/
  FlyingToasters.astro` adapts the CSS keyframe + step()-flicker
  technique from Bryan Braun's `bryanbraun/after-dark-css` project
  (https://github.com/bryanbraun/after-dark-css), MIT-licensed for
  the HTML/CSS portion.

- **After Dark sprite GIFs** — `site/public/sprites/toaster-sprite.gif`
  and `site/public/sprites/toast.gif` originate from After Dark™
  (1989), © Berkeley Systems, Inc. Re-distributed here for
  nostalgic homage; copyright remains with the original rightsholder.
